er than requested sleep time, otherwise skip sleep and defaults back to busy-loop behavior.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>On systems with boot flags <code>acpi=off</code>, clock resolution could be large (&gt;=4ms in some instances).  This leads to simulation rates at 1/4 of real-time or slower if any non-zero physics <code>&lt;update_rate&gt;</code> is specified.  Setting physics <code>&lt;update_rate&gt;</code> to 0 leads to unthrottled simulation.</p>\n<p>A <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/72/new-time-nsleep-call-sleep-will-check-to\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #72</a> has been created to check and make sure clock resolution is smaller than requested sleep time, otherwise skip sleep and defaults back to busy-loop behavior.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "John Hsu", "uuid": "{0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec/5445ce6e-6273-47f0-84eb-621c86ca11cb/128"}}, "nickname": "hsu", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec"}, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2012-10-31T19:25:59.612539+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:43:56.442354+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 178}